  "1605220": {
    "name": "Dune: Spice Wars",
    "steam_appid": 1605220,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/3dcfcf22a22e1ef639871a4dfd9c9975.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong>这沙漠以及这沙丘只属于你。</strong><br><br>玩家需要引领自己的派系，为控制和统治严酷的沙漠星球厄拉科斯而战。香料是宇宙里最至关重要的资源。这种资源香料能够延续生命，扩展意识并保证宇宙航行。这种香料只存在于厄拉科斯，得到宇宙里最具影响力的各种势力追捧……<br><br>扫描蠕虫标志环境或者冒着失去你的队伍和香料收割器的风险，因为巨型沙丘蠕虫会冲破整个沙丘并将其吞噬。在战斗中击溃他们，并利用政治阴谋战胜对手，或通过你的神秘间谍网络摧毁他们。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/b4b47d3602180c88c9e9e6c7f0f95437.poster.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/b4b47d3602180c88c9e9e6c7f0f95437.webm?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/b4b47d3602180c88c9e9e6c7f0f95437.mp4?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/ad38d9dbfcccfedc9ca74b6d40d9c318.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=100 /></span><br><br>体验独特的沙丘世界，有史以来最具影响力的科幻作品之一。扮演如公爵莱托·亚崔迪、男爵弗拉迪米尔·哈肯尼、帕迪沙皇帝沙达姆四世、埃斯马·图克以及李特·凯恩斯等标志性人物并带领你的派系走向胜利。时刻保持警惕，因为对立的派别会不惜手段取得优势，而这个星球本身也受到广域沙漠、巨大的风暴和骇人沙虫的威胁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/8dc9211c86e0384d2faff06ab4dec9c0.poster.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/8dc9211c86e0384d2faff06ab4dec9c0.webm?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/8dc9211c86e0384d2faff06ab4dec9c0.mp4?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/fdb7e4616f17b566acba2e2890fb1f98.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong>4X元素的即时游戏。</strong><br><br>平衡公开战争、潜规则、政治影响和经济优势以取得胜利并获得对宇宙中至关重要的星球的控制权！使用秘密特工来破坏你的对手的计划。在立法会议上对政治决议进行投票，进一步制定自己的策略。或者通过全面进攻压倒对手来支配他。<br><br>使用扑翼机探索厄拉科斯并找到资源、村庄以及兴趣点。扩大你的队伍并控制尽可能多的区域。通过建筑物和香料收割机开发资源并主导经济。部署太空船并摧毁你的敌人，不过请注意因为公然的侵略会带来很高的政治影响。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/aa24bce83998446c987c2dcdfe822368.poster.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/aa24bce83998446c987c2dcdfe822368.webm?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/aa24bce83998446c987c2dcdfe822368.mp4?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/346ab047aa9057efa8ffb3a193f32848.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=100 /></span><br><br>踏上一段战略之旅，您可以选择光荣与政治之路，或是拥抱暴力与欺诈。从各种拥有独特能力和玩法风格的派系中进行选择。每个派系都可以通过选择议员来增强他们的优势并减轻弱点。<br><br>无论您选择生存战术、阴暗交易、军事力量还是主导香料贸易，都有适合每位玩家偏好的派系和议员组合。在厄拉科斯上探索无限可能，塑造自己的命运。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/1766ad96f03efeb80c8cf76a2bd5843f.poster.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/1766ad96f03efeb80c8cf76a2bd5843f.webm?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/1766ad96f03efeb80c8cf76a2bd5843f.mp4?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/1a0d2c2b449b868485ccb5c7e3916d28.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong>征服模式。</strong><br><br>选择控制其中一个主要家族，并在各种独特的情景和局势中展开战斗。通过为起始家族个性化选择各种技能和升级，来应对征服模式中众多具有挑战性的目标，确保每次游戏都能获得独特的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/9814bac8cd4c07c122d36ce0af2a4197.poster.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/9814bac8cd4c07c122d36ce0af2a4197.webm?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/9814bac8cd4c07c122d36ce0af2a4197.mp4?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/6d28b88264e767fedf3ebf8c68a2570c.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=100 /></span><br><br>在2V2的比赛中团结起来共同对抗敌人，或在最多四名玩家的自由竞争中相互对峙。根据你的喜好定制多人游戏的参数，包括AI难度、地图大小、胜利条件以及沙虫的入侵、风暴和穴地数量。组队并尝试不同的派别组合，以达到协同作用并主宰厄拉科斯。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/2dd52ed4520c164116d4cc55455fef7e.poster.avif?t=1733479296\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/2dd52ed4520c164116d4cc55455fef7e.webm?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1605220/extras/2dd52ed4520c164116d4cc55455fef7e.mp4?t=1733479296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
